# GitLab Project Issues (Tickets) API - Integrations
created: 2024-01-15, last updated: 2026-02-02, [Read more](https://www.apideck.com/integrations/gitlab/collection-tickets)

Sync permissioned project issues data with GitLab through Apideck's unified API.
One integration, instant access to the governed data your team needs.
In Apideck, this resource is called Tickets (API:
`collection-tickets`)
Full CRUD support available through our unified API
...
Start syncing GitLab project issues in minutes
```
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/unify'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: process.env.APIDECK_API_KEY,
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'YOUR_CONSUMER_ID'
})
// List project issues from GitLab
const result = await apideck.issue-tracking.collectionTickets.list({
serviceId: 'gitlab'
})
for await (const page of result) {
console.log(page)
// Returns unified project issues data

